Interface TimedEntry

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Entry
All Known Subinterfaces:
AnnotationEntry, EventEntry, MeasurementEntry, SignalEntry, ValuesEntry
public interface TimedEntry
extends Entry

TimedEntry is the superclass of MeasurementEntry and EventEntry and defines their common methods.
